// Solution/aggregator (K.W2 — inv-K-1 structural split).
//
// The unified `include: ["src/", "demo/"]` was split into two programs so the
// PUBLISHED library graph (tsconfig.lib.json, `src/` only) is glass-ui-free by
// construction, while the demo graph (tsconfig.demo.json, `demo/`) resolves
// glass-ui from source. This root only references the two leaves for editor /
// `--build` ergonomics; the binding gates run each leaf with `-p … --noEmit`
// (see the `typecheck` script). No `compilerOptions`/`include` live here — they
// moved to tsconfig.base.json + the two leaves.
{
    "files": [],
    "references": [
        { "path": "./tsconfig.lib.json" },
        { "path": "./tsconfig.demo.json" }
    ]
}
